###############################################################################
# 10. TROUBLESHOOTING
###############################################################################

### Common Issues and Solutions:
#
# 1. "Unauthorized" Error:
#    - Make sure you've signed in and copied the token
#    - Update @instructorToken or @studentToken variables above
#
# 2. "Course not found":
#    - Run "Get All Courses" first to get valid course ID
#    - Update @courseId variable above
#
# 3. "Session not found":
#    - Create a session first using "Create New Session"
#    - Update @sessionId variable above
#
# 4. "Outside GPS range":
#    - This is expected! Use coordinates 37.7749, -122.4194 for success
#    - Sessions are created with 100m radius at this location
#
# 5. Service not responding:
#    - Check if all services are running:
#      * Auth Service: http://localhost:3001
#      * Attendance Service: http://localhost:3002  
#      * Realtime Service: http://localhost:3003
#
# 6. WebSocket connection fails:
#    - Make sure realtime service is running
#    - Check browser console for errors
#    - Verify JWT token is valid and not expired

###############################################################################
# 11. GPS VERIFICATION NOTES
###############################################################################

### Important GPS Information:
#
# 🔍 NO ACCESS CODES REQUIRED!
# - Students only need to be within GPS radius
# - Sessions use latitude/longitude + radius for verification
# - Default test coordinates: 37.7749, -122.4194 (San Francisco)
# - Default radius: 100 meters
#
# ✅ Valid GPS coordinates (within range):
# Latitude: 37.7749, Longitude: -122.4194
#
# ❌ Invalid GPS coordinates (outside range):
# Latitude: 37.8000, Longitude: -122.4500
#
# 📱 Real-time Events:
# - session:started - Broadcast when instructor starts session
# - attendance:marked - Broadcast when student marks attendance
# - All events include GPS distance information

###############################################################################
# END OF TEST HUB
###############################################################################
